    <item>
      <title>Cboe 的徐先生表示，股市抛售是由流动性驱动的</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-05/stock-market-selloff-is-liquidity-driven-cboe-s-xu-says-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Cboe 衍生品市场情报主管 Mandy Xu 表示，周五的市场抛售更多是由基本面因素推动的，而非周一的抛售。她在彭博电视台发表讲话。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-05/stock-market-selloff-is-liquidity-driven-cboe-s-xu-says-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 14:37:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>吸金数十亿美元的科技 ETF 惨遭 60% 亏损</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/tech-etfs-that-drew-billions-are-battered-by-losses-hitting-60</link>
      <description><![CDATA[上个月，交易员投入了数十亿美元押注科技股大幅反弹。如今，他们杠杆率较高的 ETF 头寸在市场全面崩盘中遭受重创。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/tech-etfs-that-drew-billions-are-battered-by-losses-hitting-60</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 14:34:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Crossmark 的 Fernandez 建议今天休息一下</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-05/take-a-break-today-says-crossmark-s-fernandez-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Crossmark Global Investments 首席市场策略师维多利亚·费尔南德斯 (Victoria Fernandez) 表示，投资者今天可能希望在此次抛售期间“稍事休息”。 (来源：彭博社)]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-05/take-a-break-today-says-crossmark-s-fernandez-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 14:32:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>全球市场危机加剧，大宗商品面临危机蔓延</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/commodities-face-contagion-as-global-market-meltdown-deepens</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着全球金融市场危机的扩大，从铜、黄金到原油等大宗商品价格大幅下跌，交易员纷纷套现获利，并在工业原材料市场进行新的看跌押注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/commodities-face-contagion-as-global-market-meltdown-deepens</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 14:25:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>大陆集团考虑分拆汽车零部件业务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/continental-weighs-spinning-off-struggling-automotive-unit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[大陆集团可能会将其陷入困境的汽车零部件业务与更为成功的轮胎业务分开，这将成为这家德国公司 152 年历史上最大的重组。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/continental-weighs-spinning-off-struggling-automotive-unit</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 11:40:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
