      <title>凯雷交易退出相关利润因市场低迷而下滑 12%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/carlyle-s-profit-tied-to-exiting-deals-falls-12-in-muted-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[凯雷集团 (Carlyle Group Inc.) 在收购交易商业务不景气的时期内，通过套现赌注获得的利润较少。]]></description>
