      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/libya-s-sharara-oil-field-output-declines-to-about-100-000-b-d</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据两位知情人士透露，利比亚最大的油田于周一停止生产，此前运营商被迫在周末逐步减产。]]></description>
